            <h2>Top Pick #1 — FreeModel (Multi-Model Gateway)</h2>
            <p><a href="https://freemodel.dev/invite/FRE-7a3b6220" target="_blank" rel="sponsored noopener"><strong>FreeModel</strong></a> is the strongest pick for developers who want to ship without committing to a single provider. The platform sits in front of a pool of open-source frontier models (DeepSeek V3/R1, GLM, Qwen, Kimi, Llama, Mistral) and routes each request to the one most likely to nail it. Your existing OpenAI SDK or Anthropic SDK works with just a base URL swap.</p>
            <p><strong>Why this beats picking a single provider:</strong></p>
            <ul>
              <li>You write code once. FreeModel picks the best model per task.</li>
              <li>If DeepSeek is rate-limited, request auto-falls-back to GLM or Qwen.</li>
              <li>You can pin or exclude specific providers at any time (compliance, preference).</li>
              <li>China developers get direct connectivity — no proxy required.</li>
            </ul>
            <p><strong>Free tier:</strong> Email or Google signup, free credits on verification, no card required. <strong>Affiliate disclosure:</strong> APIRank is a FreeModel affiliate — the signup link above includes our tracking.</p>
