            <p><a href="https://openrouter.ai/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><strong>OpenRouter</strong></a> is the strongest pick for developers who want to browse the frontier model landscape without paying for each one individually. The platform catalogs 400+ models, and 13+ are marked with `:free` at time of writing — including NVIDIA Nemotron 3 Ultra (1M-token context, frontier reasoning) and OpenAI's gpt-oss-120b.</p>
            <p><strong>Why OpenRouter's free tier works:</strong></p>
            <ul>
              <li>One API key, OpenAI-compatible endpoint — drop-in for any existing OpenAI SDK.</li>
              <li>You can browse 13+ frontier-tier models without paying anything.</li>
              <li>If you find a model you like, upgrade to paid tier on the same provider without changing code.</li>
              <li>The <a href="/tutorials/openrouter-fusion-api-2026/">OpenRouter Fusion API</a> and <a href="/tutorials/openrouter-mcp-server-2026/">MCP server</a> extend the platform's capabilities for production use.</li>
            </ul>
