            <p><a href="https://aistudio.google.com/apikey" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><strong>Google AI Studio</strong></a> is the strongest pick for developers who need a production-grade free tier from a major lab. The free API key unlocks Gemini 2.5 Pro (1M-token context), Gemini 2.5 Flash, Gemini 2.0 Flash, and the older 1.5 Pro/Flash models. No credit card. Multimodal input (text, image, audio, video) all supported.</p>
